      "text": "2. Front upper grille removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000842",
          "label": "Front upper grille removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Bumper beam removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583094_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the harness clamp (A) on the A/C compressor and remove the bumper beam."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Intercooler Guide B removal (turbo charger equipped vehicles)"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583095_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Reserve tank removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583096_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Radiator Fan/Shroud Assy. removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583097_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A) and remove the clamp (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583098_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A) and remove the clamp (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583099_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Remove the water filler mounting bolt (A). Disconnect the coupler (B) and remove the clamp (C). Remove the radiator upper bracket (D)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583101_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "Shift the radiator/condenser assy. and remove the radiator fan/shroud assy. while rotating it."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. Fan Shroud Assy. resolution"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "437_5.0_jpn_11583102_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    }
